(59, 1, '2016-04-13 12:26:38', '2016-04-13 06:56:38', '<img class=\"size-full wp-image-202 alignleft\" src=\"http://www.pixelplosion.com/sites/lifesupportncare/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Emergency4.jpg\" alt=\"Emergency4\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /> Our execution strategy incorporates proven methodologies, highly qualified, internationally accredited personnel, and a highly responsive approach to managing deliverables. Following is a description of our training methods, including how it will be carried out effectively.\r\n\r\nThe LS&amp;NC approach to education provides all course participants a dynamic balance of hands-on skills training and informative lectures. All LS&amp;NC training programs include the following:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Expert instruction from experienced and qualified trainers with a low student to instructor ratio.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The latest internationally recognized guidelines and training, taught by subject area experts and experienced medical care providers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Hands-on skills training made possible by our state-of-the-art simulation lab and up-to-date, international standard materials and equipment.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Strategy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'strategy', '', '', '2016-06-23 12:33:54', '2016-06-23 07:03:54', '', 6, 'http://www.pixelplosion.com/sites/lifesupportncare/?page_id=59', 0, 'page', '', 0),
