(149, 1, '2016-04-16 10:23:08', '2016-04-16 04:53:08', 'Our execution strategy incorporates proven methodologies, highly qualified, internationally accredited personnel, and a highly responsive approach to managing deliverables. Following is a description of our training methods, including how it will be carried out effectively.\r\n\r\nThe LS&amp;NC approach to education provides all course participants a dynamic balance of hands-on skills training and informative lectures. All LS&amp;NC training programs include the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Expert instruction from experienced and qualified trainers with a low student to instructor ratio.</li></br>\r\n 	<li>The latest internationally recognized guidelines and training, taught by subject area experts and experienced medical care providers.</li></br>\r\n 	<li>Hands-on skills training made possible by our state-of-the-art simulation lab and up-to-date, international standard materials and equipment.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Stratergy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '59-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-16 10:23:08', '2016-04-16 04:53:08', '', 59, 'http://www.pixelplosion.com/sites/lifesupportncare/2016/04/16/59-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
