(179, 1, '2016-04-24 22:17:25', '2016-04-24 16:47:25', 'Our team of young professionals has been involved in hands on training since the year 2012 with the world’s number one emergency medical service provider, Falck in Sri Lanka. They have been trained under a British Doctor and Australian Paramedic and have undergone intensive and up to date training. Dr. Michelle Benedict was in charge of the Falck Training Centre handling of both internal and external training. Mr. Elger Isaac &amp; Mrs. Thuwaraha Chandrakumar functioned as external trainers.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-132\" style=\"float: left; margin-right: 20px\" src=\"http://www.pixelplosion.com/sites/lifesupportncare/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Pic1-300x175.jpg\" alt=\"Pic1\" width=\"300\" height=\"175\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-133\" src=\"http://www.pixelplosion.com/sites/lifesupportncare/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Pic2-300x175.jpg\" alt=\"Pic2\" width=\"300\" height=\"175\" />\r\n\r\nWhilst working with Falck, they have trained numerous numbers of companies, hotels, NGOs, schools and individuals. A few of these organizations are listed below:\r\n\r\n<strong>Schools:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>St. Thomas’s College</li>\r\n 	<li>Gateway College</li>\r\n 	<li>British School (on going)</li>\r\n 	<li>Overseas School</li>\r\n 	<li>Al-Iman International School</li>\r\n 	<li>Elizabeth Moir</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Nurseries:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Joyce Gunesekara’s Montessori</li>\r\n 	<li>Jittabugs Nursery &amp; Daycare Centre</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Companies:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Dialog (on going)</li>\r\n 	<li>Sierra</li>\r\n 	<li>Holcim (on going)</li>\r\n 	<li>Iluka (on going)</li>\r\n 	<li>Malwatte Plantations</li>\r\n 	<li>Seals – outdoor company</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Hotels:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Hilton (on going)</li>\r\n 	<li>Mount Lavinia</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Special Projects:</strong> We have provided Ambulance services for Holc